YOUR ANSWERS ARE JUST BEYOND THE HORIZON.
Trade Horizons is a quarterly publication produced by
the PIERS Maritime Research Group. This publication
provides a two-year history, forecasts and analysis of
trade between 60 major trading partners and the U.S.
To order the recently published Fall 2001 issue,
please call 800-952-3839 ext. 7062 or visit
