moving containers between the Pacific and Atlantic oceans.
http://news.joc.com/cgi-bin7/flo?y=eD8A0BejkZ0BbA0SLM0AB

NYK INAUGURATES S. AMER.-HOUSTON BULK, RO-RO SERVICE
The line opened monthly breakbulk and ro-ro service to
South America from the Port of Houston.
http://news.joc.com/cgi-bin7/flo?y=eD8A0BejkZ0BbA0SLN0AC

HOWLAND HOOK TO REOPEN LOGISTICS FACILITY
A warehouse and logistics facility is opened at the
New York terminal.
http://news.joc.com/cgi-bin7/flo?y=eD8A0BejkZ0BbA0SLO0AD

